      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/iniciando-meu-blog-com-hugo-pt-2/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;dando-vida-ao-meu-blog-um-guia-prático-com-hugo-pt-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;center&gt;Dando Vida ao Meu Blog: Um Guia Prático com &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; [Pt-2]&lt;/center&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#dando-vida-ao-meu-blog-um-guia-pr%c3%a1tico-com-hugo-pt-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link para o cabeçalho&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link para o cabeçalho&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Dando continuidade ao post &lt;a href=&#34;https://rafaeljesus.dev.br/posts/iniciando-meu-blog-com-hugo&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;anterior&lt;/a&gt;, vamos finalizar as configurações que implementam o &lt;strong&gt;Meu Blog&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Em resumo o que fizemos no &lt;strong&gt;post&lt;/strong&gt; anterior foi:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Instalar a linguagem &lt;a href=&#34;https://go.dev/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Go&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Instalar o &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Configurar o repositório no &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/B4bayaga/rafaeljesus.github.io&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Instalar o &lt;a href=&#34;https://themes.gohugo.io/themes/hugo-coder/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Theme&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Configurar DNS do Domínio.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Configurar o &lt;a href=&#34;https://pages.github.com/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;GitHub Pages&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Com isso o &lt;strong&gt;blog&lt;/strong&gt; está no ar e disponível para todo o planeta.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Dando Vida ao Meu Blog [Pt-1]</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/iniciando-meu-blog-com-hugo-pt-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Jun 2025 10:21:35 -0300</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/iniciando-meu-blog-com-hugo-pt-1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;dando-vida-ao-meu-blog-um-guia-prático-com-hugo-pt-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;center&gt;Dando Vida ao Meu Blog: Um Guia Prático com &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; (Pt-1)&lt;/center&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#dando-vida-ao-meu-blog-um-guia-pr%c3%a1tico-com-hugo-pt-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link para o cabeçalho&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link para o cabeçalho&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Para começar, qual tecnologia usar para construir e publicar o &lt;strong&gt;Meu Blog&lt;/strong&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A resposta para essa pergunta foi francamente difícil devido à vasta quantidade de opções existentes. E logo de cara, pensei em construir com ferramentas que &amp;ldquo;domino&amp;rdquo; (na data que escrevo este artigo), que são &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.python.org/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Python&lt;/a&gt; com &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.djangoproject.com/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Django&lt;/a&gt;, depois obviamente pensei em &lt;a href=&#34;https://wordpress.org/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Wordpress&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://plone.org/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Plone&lt;/a&gt; entre outras. Passei uma semana inteira apenas para escolher que tecnologia usar, e foi quando vi um post do &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/akitaonrails&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Fabio Akita&lt;/a&gt;, no post, ele descrevia como foi migrar o seu blog &lt;a href=&#34;https://akitaonrails.com/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;AkitaOnRails&lt;/a&gt;, salvo engano escrito em &lt;a href=&#34;https://rubyonrails.org/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Rails&lt;/a&gt;, para usar o &lt;strong&gt;Hugo&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
